I seem to have no problems in  place like KC when resident level 50 group of tards with wurmslayers wants a camp and im sitting there with a shaman/cleric/druid owning it. For the simple fact that people know I was there first, they dont care that I can clear hmm, lemme count: 4+5+4+4=17 mobs in before a respawn. <br>
<br>
Why should a normal seb group care if 3x the amount of people are killing 3x the amount of mobs. What would you say if you zoned to seb and disco was camped by prien and warlor, NG by me and random shaman_01, jail by some other 2man combo. Would you send us tells asking if you can have our camp, because 6 people should hold 3 camps?<br>
