GD socialist, treehugging, self righteous pos.  Actually I like the Sierra Club so strike the tree hugger part.  If you want socialism go to Greece but keep your redistribution schemes out of eq.  As a film critic beating up the movie D&amp;D, D&amp;D was about killing kobolds and taking loot not solving world problems.  EQ isn't much different.  <br>
