AoE group is the equivalent of a group with m60 machine guns and most 55ish groups have pistols.  There are a lot of mobs to kill who keep popping back up on a reasonably short timer.<br>
<br>
Honestly, which of the two groups is best apt to get the job done? It isn't about justice, or equity,  its superior firepower earned through levels and aaxp v. someone that hasn't put in the time yet wanting a piece of someone elses pie.  <br>
<br>
I think its great that there are a few zone you can go to and do AoE.  If you are not uber enough (is uber still a word?) to do Seb King, Crypt or Juggs which are rarely camped all at same time go do a zone like Chardok where you can always find loot and good xp and not camp steal casters your are terribly jealous of. <br>
<br>
